			<p> Email: <a href="Trisophic-Union@protonmail.com">Trisophic-Union@protonmail.com</a></p>
			<p> Github: <a href="https://github.com/Trisophic-Union">https://github.com/Trisophic-Union</a> </p>
			<p> Instagram: <a href="https://www.instagram.com/trisophic_union/">https://www.instagram.com/trisophic_union/</a></p>
			<p> Mastodon: <a href="https://mastodon.social/@trisophic_union">https://mastodon.social/@trisophic_union</a> </p>
			<p> Youtube: <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Trisophicunion">https://www.youtube.com/@Trisophicunion</a> </p>
		</span>
	</footer>
</Layout>

